ğŸ® Tic-Tac-Toe Game in Python

This is a simple Tic-Tac-Toe exercise developed in Python using the Tkinter library for the graphical interface.

Features:

Two-player game (X and O)

Graphical interface with buttons

Win and tie detection

Restart game button

Exercise goal:
Practice programming logic, functions, conditionals, and building graphical interfaces with Tkinter.
